Name: Increase price of top sellers

Short Description: Manager increases the prices of the 3 top sellers of the last 30 days.

Precondition: There have been sales in the last 30 days.

Postcondition: The price of the top sellers are increased by 5%.

Error Condition: No sales where made in the last 30 days.

System state on error condition: No prices are increased.

Actors: Manager

Trigger: Manager wishes to earn more money.

Standard procedure:
(1) Managers views the top sellers.
(2) Manager clicks the increase button.
(3) Prices are increased.
